##PLAY
#XF86AudioPlay
#    playerctl play-pause
#
##Next
#XF86AudioNext
#    playerctl next
#
##previous
#XF86AudioPrev
#    playerctl previous
#
##Stop
#XF86AudioStop
#    playerctl stop
#
